PrecisAmendments to the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES which replace the current Arrest Warrant form with one specifically authorizing entry into a dwelling-house to effect the arrest, authorize courts martial to issue Judicial Arrest Warrants (non-appearance of accused) and prescribe the form to be used.
